@startuml
|User|
start
: Click on Update button;
|System|
:Display form to Update Employee;
|User|
repeat: Fill needed information;
: Click on Confirm button;
|System|
: Validate Updated Data;
backward: Show error message;
repeat while (is Data valid?) is (no) not (yes)
: Update Employee;
: Update Employee details screen;
stop
@enduml
